  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9b0de1441a190476f84d46203267d169, type: 3}
  m_Name: AkimDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  Lines:
  - "Ha! There you are \u2014 the guitarist himself. So... how\u2019s life in this
    charming dump treating you?"
  - "Don\u2019t bother answering. I know \u2014 this place makes a rat look like
    royalty."
  - "But hey, I\u2019ve got a ticket out. Bright lights, big city\u2026 the whole
    shebang if you know what I mean."
  - "Step one: that ancient Golf by the wall. Been rotting there longer than my Uncle
    Vinnie\u2019s career. I know a mechanic next door \u2014 can help\u2026 but he
    can\u2019t stand me \u2014 hates my guts for no reason."
  - "If you can grab his tools, I\u2019ll help get it running. So\u2026 you in or
    what?"
